<span style='float: right; width: 280px; height: 187px; margin: 0 0 5px 5px; border: 1px solid black;'><script type='text/javascript'>flash_object ('http://graphics.millsberry.com/buddy/buddy_featured.swf', '280', '187', 'userName=marnar&buddyTimeStamp=20050822&buddyScriptURL=http%3A%2F%2Fmillsberry.com%2Fbuddy%2Fprocess_buddy.phtml&unixTimeStamp=1193060140&serverTimeOffset=28800', '', 'exactfit', 'transparent');</script></span>
Meet <b>Maris</b>, our citizen of the week!<br>	<br>Maris lives at <a href='/home/?user=marnar'>22886 Central Avenue</a> in the trendiest area of Metro Park, and though she's only lived in Millsberry for a few months, Maris already knows her way around town like a pro!<br><br>When Maris starts school at <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/academy/">Millsberry Academy</a> this fall, she won't have to worry about making new friends, since she's already made quite a few!  Maris is very friendly, and her bubbly personality makes her an instant hit wherever she goes.  She especially enjoys meeting new people when playing team sports.  Maris thinks that working together as a team is a great way to get to know someone.  That's why it's no surprise that she's met many of her best friends while playing her favorite sport, soccer.  Whenever she's out on the soccer field, Maris is sure to be wearing one of her three favorite pairs of cleats (which are green, orange, and light blue) for good luck.  She also enjoys spending time with her friends doing other athletic activities, though, such as going for long hikes through the woods of Golden Valley and all around <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/sylvane_lake/">Sylvane Lake</a>.  <br><br>Maris is also very creative, and she likes to challenge herself by putting that creativity to use in many unique ways.  For example, Maris is great at planning parties and likes to help out with everything, from deciding on the menu to making decorations.   She always remembers to get everyone involved, though, so that nobody feels left out.  Maris also likes to use her creativity in more traditional ways; one of her dreams is to paint a huge mural with her friends for all of Millsberry to enjoy.<br><br>Maris's favorite outlet for her creativity, however, is singing.  She always brings something new and exciting to any song that she performs.  Maris's singing style has been most influenced by pop, country, and punk songs, giving her performances a soulful yet fun quality - a perfect match for her personality!  Maris has already done some musical experimentation at the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/studio/">Millsberry Recording Studio</a>, and her originality has really paid off!  Thanks to her unmistakable sound, she's already had a hit on the Cinnamon Toast Crunch Top Ten chart, and more chart-topping successes are certain to follow.<br><br>During summer, Maris spends most of her free time swimming.  She finds that pools are ideal hangouts, because they allow her to indulge her athletic side with swimming and diving, while still pleasing her more laidback side with sunbathing and just splashing around with her friends.  When it gets too cold for swimming, Maris and her friends head indoors to catch a new movie at the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/complex/">Downtown Entertainment Complex</a> or to do a little window-shopping at a mall.<br><br>Thanks for being a fine citizen, Maris, and congratulations on being named Millsberry's citizen of the week!</div>
